Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:01.29,0:00:03.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,梦…梦终止的日子…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:04.30,0:00:07.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就像雪在春天的阳光中\N溶化消失一般
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:07.90,0:00:12.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就像回忆在永远的时光中\N朦胧消失一般
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:12.87,0:00:16.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,现在…漫长的梦…\N诉说着结束…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:16.71,0:00:18.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,最后…唯一一个…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:18.31,0:00:20.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我的愿望是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:48.51,0:00:54.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没有时间的黄昏的天空
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:58.72,0:01:05.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,进行着一段永远的旅程
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:09.80,0:01:19.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,冰冷的指尖继续探索着
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:19.84,0:01:24.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,碎片发出光芒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:25.28,0:01:31.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,紧紧的抱住胸口
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:33.45,0:01:38.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,寻找遗失的东西
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:38.46,0:01:43.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,用双手的掌心确认
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:44.13,0:01:49.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,相遇在新的早晨
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:49.54,0:01:57.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,时间开始流动了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:05.22,0:02:06.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,「梦的痕迹」
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:15.66,0:02:16.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,欢迎回来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:17.13,0:02:19.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妈妈说因为工作的关系\N会晚点回来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:19.53,0:02:21.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,叫我们先…吃…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:22.54,0:02:24.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,佑…一…？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:27.11,0:02:28.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,佑一
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:30.34,0:02:32.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我做了咖哩饭了…要吃吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:32.95,0:02:33.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不 不用了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:34.11,0:02:36.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不吃的话对身体不好喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:36.68,0:02:40.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,期末考也快到了\N要是身体弄坏的话…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:40.32,0:02:41.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,吵死了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:41.59,0:02:43.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不是说我不要了吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:46.09,0:02:47.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,对不起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:47.43,0:02:50.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果想吃的话 就来跟我说吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:51.33,0:02:52.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可恶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:18.86,0:03:19.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,亚由？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:19.73,0:03:21.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,佑一 你迟到了唷
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:22.63,0:03:23.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,亚由
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:23.93,0:03:25.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,佑一
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:26.67,0:03:28.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,亚由
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:30.70,0:03:32.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,为什么…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:32.87,0:03:36.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,为什么我\N一直到现在都没想起来呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:36.54,0:03:39.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这么…这么重要的事情…\N为什么…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:39.55,0:03:41.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可恶…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:44.95,0:03:47.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,早上 早上了唷
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:50.19,0:03:52.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,「我到森林去」
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:59.00,0:04:02.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,听说这棵树七年前被锯掉了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:03.47,0:04:04.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,名雪…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:06.01,0:04:09.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,原本是从街上的任何一个角落\N都可以看得见的大树呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:11.04,0:04:12.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:12.81,0:04:14.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我想起来了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:14.28,0:04:16.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,七年前从这棵树上
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:16.15,0:04:18.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,掉下来的一个女孩子的事情
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:19.65,0:04:21.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她是在这里认识的小女孩
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:21.49,0:04:24.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,总是流露出很寂寞的眼神
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:24.32,0:04:26.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,佑一 你看
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:26.43,0:04:28.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好漂亮的夕阳
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:31.20,0:04:32.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,明天还有后天
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:33.07,0:04:36.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果能一直和佑一\N一起看这个夕阳就好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:37.00,0:04:38.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果再放假的话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:38.64,0:04:41.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我答应你\N我会再到你这里玩的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:45.18,0:04:49.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,佑一 愿望…还剩下两个对吧？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:50.62,0:04:53.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那么第二个愿望
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:53.29,0:04:56.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我想要跟佑一\N一起上同样的学校
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:56.99,0:04:58.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,亚由…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:58.22,0:05:00.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,跟佑一一起在一样的学校
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:00.99,0:05:02.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一起念书…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:02.70,0:05:04.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一起吃中餐…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:04.53,0:05:05.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一起扫地…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:05.83,0:05:09.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,然后 想跟佑一一起回家…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:09.47,0:05:11.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这种愿望不行吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:12.20,0:05:13.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我知道了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:13.27,0:05:14.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那么现在开始
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:14.84,0:05:16.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这里就是\N只属于我们两人的学校
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:16.91,0:05:19.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没有老师\N也没有讨厌的作业跟考试
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:19.95,0:05:21.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,想休息就休息
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:21.81,0:05:23.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,想玩就玩
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:23.68,0:05:24.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好棒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:24.55,0:05:25.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那…午餐呢？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:25.89,0:05:27.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可以吃自己想吃的东西喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:27.82,0:05:28.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那我要鲷鱼烧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:29.05,0:05:31.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,该不会每天都是鲷鱼烧吧？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:31.72,0:05:32.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,也可以啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:32.66,0:05:34.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,反正是\N只属于我们两人的学校嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:36.23,0:05:38.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,明天也在学校见面吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:41.73,0:05:43.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,约好了…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:43.47,0:05:44.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,从那天开始
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:44.54,0:05:46.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们就约在这森林里见面了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:47.24,0:05:50.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,每天每天 玩到太阳下山为止
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:56.48,0:05:57.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,亚由 你迟到了喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:00.42,0:06:02.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,佑一 对不起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:02.79,0:06:05.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我在找这个
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:05.42,0:06:06.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,玻璃瓶？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:06.99,0:06:08.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,佑一
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:08.16,0:06:10.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,用这个来做时光胶囊吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:10.60,0:06:12.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,时光胶囊？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:12.13,0:06:13.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,把我们的回忆
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:13.97,0:06:16.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,放到这个里面对起来放好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:16.84,0:06:18.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你…那个是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:18.60,0:06:21.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,虽然愿望还剩下一个\N但是也没关系
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:21.81,0:06:24.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因为我现在已经够幸福了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:24.78,0:06:27.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,剩下的一个\N是要留给将来的自己
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:27.35,0:06:32.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,或许不一定是自己\N而是送给其它的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:32.95,0:06:35.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不做记号找得到吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:35.99,0:06:36.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,找得到的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:37.06,0:06:40.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只要有人打从心里\N需要这个人偶的话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:47.73,0:06:49.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,佑…一…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:49.77,0:06:52.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不要说话 现在送你去医院…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:54.94,0:06:57.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,对不起 我掉下来了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:58.01,0:07:00.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,亏我还对爬树很拿手的说…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:00.98,0:07:02.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,亚由…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:02.65,0:07:04.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不要露出那种表情
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:05.02,0:07:08.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没问题的 我一点都不痛的…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:09.29,0:07:10.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,振作一点啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:10.66,0:07:12.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我为了你买了这…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:12.86,0:07:15.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我买了这个来给你的喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:17.80,0:07:19.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,给…给我…？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:20.30,0:07:22.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你如果不要我就要丢掉了喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:22.33,0:07:24.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢你佑一…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:24.30,0:07:27.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,下次我一定会戴着这个\N跟你见面的…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:28.04,0:07:30.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你还会跟我玩吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:31.54,0:07:33.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那…打勾勾…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:35.81,0:07:37.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你看 打勾勾了喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:37.68,0:07:39.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,约好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:39.18,0:07:41.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,已经约好了要再在一起玩的喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:42.29,0:07:46.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢…佑一…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:50.93,0:07:52.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不会吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:52.50,0:07:53.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,开玩笑的吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:53.87,0:07:54.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,亚由？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:55.03,0:07:57.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,亚由
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:04.18,0:08:06.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那个女孩是…亚由…？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:06.41,0:08:08.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那个时光胶囊里面
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:08.58,0:08:11.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,应该是只装着快乐的回忆的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:11.78,0:08:14.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不要发生那种事情的话…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:15.25,0:08:16.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我很卑鄙对不对？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:17.02,0:08:18.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我…我不是忘记了…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:18.66,0:08:20.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,而是想要不记得一切…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:20.49,0:08:23.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不想记得亚由已经不在这世上…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:23.26,0:08:26.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她明明一直都在找那个人偶…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:27.20,0:08:29.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,佑一 来找找看吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:31.37,0:08:32.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,亚由她…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:32.77,0:08:36.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在找那个天使模样的人偶对吧？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:36.28,0:08:40.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那么 就让我们亲手替她找吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:41.58,0:08:43.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,找人偶…？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:44.68,0:08:48.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,放心啦 佑一一定找得到的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:50.09,0:08:51.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好 来找吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:52.26,0:08:54.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什么？找东西？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:54.36,0:08:55.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,需要人手啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:55.89,0:08:57.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,比起我一个人 多一点比较好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:57.90,0:09:00.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在这种期末忙的要死的时候
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:00.30,0:09:02.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你在说什么啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:02.67,0:09:04.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,明明就没在念书
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:04.74,0:09:06.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好啊 我可以帮你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:06.74,0:09:07.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,香里
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:07.87,0:09:10.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有困难的时候就要互相帮助嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:10.91,0:09:12.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢你 香里
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:13.01,0:09:14.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,拿你没办法
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:14.25,0:09:16.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我知道了 帮忙就可以了吧？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:16.42,0:09:18.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,北川 谢谢你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:22.69,0:09:25.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真的埋在这里吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:26.46,0:09:28.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没有什么标记之类的吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:28.96,0:09:32.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只记得确实是埋在\N很大的树旁边的…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:32.40,0:09:34.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那么…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:35.00,0:09:36.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就跟没有没两样呢…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:53.79,0:09:56.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没问题 一定找得到的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:56.19,0:10:00.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只要有打从心里\N需要这个人偶的人在的话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:16.98,0:10:19.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,相泽 是不是这个啊？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:19.55,0:10:20.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,找到了吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:20.81,0:10:22.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就是这个…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:22.31,0:10:23.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎么样？是不是呢？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:32.99,0:10:34.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,找到了…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:36.96,0:10:39.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,太好了 相泽同学
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:39.16,0:10:41.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,学校餐厅的大碗咖哩饭…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:41.67,0:10:43.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,打扫的轮班…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:43.77,0:10:46.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,还有帮我写报告\N代价就是这些
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:47.41,0:10:48.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我知道了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:48.31,0:10:49.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就这么说定
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:50.01,0:10:52.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那么 我们就回去吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:52.38,0:10:55.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不行 我要先去医院后再回家
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:55.85,0:10:57.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真是冷淡啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:57.98,0:10:59.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,再见了 名雪
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:59.38,0:11:01.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,香里 北川同学 谢谢你们
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:03.22,0:11:06.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,佑一 我们也快点回去吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:20.27,0:11:22.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,脏掉了呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:22.44,0:11:24.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,毕竟都埋在土里七年了嘛…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:26.75,0:11:28.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我来把它修好吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:29.58,0:11:30.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可以吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:30.75,0:11:33.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我想应该有办法吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:33.29,0:11:34.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那就拜托你了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:34.62,0:11:35.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那么…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:35.32,0:11:38.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这个就拜托你了可以吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:38.16,0:11:39.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,OK
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:40.69,0:11:43.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,终于找到了的亚由在找的东西
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:43.20,0:11:45.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,虽然不是这样\N亚由就可以回来了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:45.93,0:11:48.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是七年前发生的那件事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:48.17,0:11:51.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我觉得可以去重新正视它了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:55.77,0:11:57.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你好 这里是水濑家…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:57.91,0:11:59.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妈
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:59.44,0:12:03.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,工作拖到很晚\N现在刚到车站
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:03.18,0:12:05.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有什么想吃的东西吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:05.32,0:12:09.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,现在佑一正在做呢…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:10.42,0:12:13.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我被拜托做事情啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:13.23,0:12:15.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什么都不用 赶快回来吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:15.89,0:12:17.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是 是 挂断啰
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:37.25,0:12:39.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没关系 名雪 我来接
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:40.49,0:12:42.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你好 这里是水濑家
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:43.82,0:12:45.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是的 没有错…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:46.39,0:12:47.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,请 请稍等一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:47.89,0:12:48.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,地点是？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:49.06,0:12:50.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是的…是的…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:50.80,0:12:53.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我了解了…谢谢你…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:53.60,0:12:54.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:54.60,0:12:56.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,秋子阿姨她…出事了…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:20.63,0:13:22.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妈妈…妈妈
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:22.96,0:13:24.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,病人需要静养 请安静一点
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:26.40,0:13:28.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你们是家属吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:28.90,0:13:30.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,情况相当危险
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:30.90,0:13:33.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,恐怕这两三天\N是最关键的时期
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:33.74,0:13:35.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎么会…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:35.84,0:13:38.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,性命或许可以保住
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:38.18,0:13:41.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是意识是否能回复就…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:41.28,0:13:45.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,总之 请尽快联络家里的亲戚
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:48.52,0:13:50.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我已经打电话给老妈了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:50.56,0:13:52.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那边好像也是天气很糟
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:52.99,0:13:54.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,机场也被对锁
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:54.36,0:13:56.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,听说飞机也不知道何时才能飞
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:57.13,0:13:59.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真是伤脑筋啊\N在这种时候却居然在海外…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:02.10,0:14:03.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不用担心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:03.24,0:14:05.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,秋子阿姨一定不会有事的啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:05.90,0:14:08.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一直 都在一起的…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:09.21,0:14:12.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我虽然不记得爸爸的脸
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:12.78,0:14:15.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是因为有妈妈温柔的笑容
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:15.61,0:14:17.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以不觉得寂寞
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:18.18,0:14:19.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因为有妈妈在
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:19.82,0:14:22.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以我才能一直笑着努力着走过来的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:23.02,0:14:25.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,学校也是 家里也是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:26.53,0:14:29.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是我已经变成了孤单一人…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:29.73,0:14:30.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你在说什么啊？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:31.03,0:14:33.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,秋子阿姨不可能会死的吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:33.17,0:14:36.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她怎么会丢下你\N自己一个人先走啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:36.33,0:14:38.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,而且我也在这边 所以…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:38.64,0:14:41.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,为什么…\N你说得出那种话呢…？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:41.81,0:14:42.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,名雪？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:43.01,0:14:48.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,佑一可以让奇迹发生\N然后救妈妈吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:50.38,0:14:52.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不可能的…对吧…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:55.19,0:14:58.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你…不是鼓励过我吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:59.19,0:15:03.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,说「为了亚由\N去找天使的人偶吧」的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:03.16,0:15:05.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在背后推我一把不是吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:05.63,0:15:07.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,当时的笑容怎么了呢？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:08.90,0:15:10.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什么嘛…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:11.30,0:15:14.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我…已经变得笑不出来了…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:17.01,0:15:19.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我最差劲了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:19.28,0:15:22.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在森林里鼓励佑一的时候也是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:22.18,0:15:25.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,其实我那时心里\N是觉得松了一口气
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:25.62,0:15:28.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因为我知道亚由已经不在了…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:29.89,0:15:31.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因为佑一的眼里…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:31.76,0:15:34.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,总是只有亚由一个人而已啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:34.79,0:15:36.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我说什么为了亚由…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:36.29,0:15:39.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,找天使人偶的话都是假的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:39.83,0:15:47.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,其实只是因为不想看到佑一\N总是为了亚由而心情低落而已
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:47.84,0:15:49.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,名雪…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:49.51,0:15:51.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我已经笑不出来了…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:52.04,0:15:54.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,已经坚强不起来了…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:54.15,0:15:56.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果妈妈不在了的话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:56.38,0:15:59.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我…就变成…一个人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:04.12,0:16:05.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一直都没有注意到…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:06.12,0:16:07.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,名雪的心情…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:08.53,0:16:11.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,七年前的…那个时候一定也是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:15.83,0:16:17.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,终于找到了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:18.54,0:16:19.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,名雪
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:19.87,0:16:22.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我一直在找你唷
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:22.31,0:16:25.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因为有东西要送给你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:25.38,0:16:27.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这个 叫做「雪兔」哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:28.65,0:16:29.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因为我笨手笨脚的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:29.75,0:16:31.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,花了很多时间不过…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:31.55,0:16:34.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是我很努力做出来的哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:35.35,0:16:37.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,还会再来见我的吧？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:38.42,0:16:40.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,虽然一直说不出口
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:40.49,0:16:42.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我对佑一…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:42.59,0:16:43.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啰唆
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:56.47,0:17:00.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我一直都无视名雪的感受吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:01.65,0:17:03.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,相泽同学
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:03.32,0:17:05.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我听说那件意外了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:05.28,0:17:06.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,还好吧？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:07.45,0:17:10.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果发生什么事 会再连络通知的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:10.79,0:17:12.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不是这个意思…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:12.39,0:17:15.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,名雪她…一个人没有关系吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:17.70,0:17:18.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:18.86,0:17:21.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,从很久以前\N就已经知道相泽同学你了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:21.60,0:17:24.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因为名雪总是兴高采烈的\N说着你的事情
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:24.74,0:17:25.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这样啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:25.70,0:17:28.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,名雪说佑一很容易害羞\N所以虽然看来不太容易亲近
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:28.47,0:17:29.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但其实是很温柔的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:29.84,0:17:31.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,虽然好几年没见面了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:31.31,0:17:33.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是一定一点都没有变…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:34.21,0:17:37.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真的是\N听她说了不知道有多少次…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:39.05,0:17:40.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这样啊…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:40.89,0:17:43.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,名雪她在你来到这个城市之前
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:43.72,0:17:46.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就已经一直在期待着\N你的到来了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:52.00,0:17:53.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,相泽同学
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:54.40,0:17:55.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,干嘛？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:55.60,0:17:58.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,请你要好好守护名雪
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:03.34,0:18:04.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我回来了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:10.18,0:18:11.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那个人偶啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:11.52,0:18:13.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是可以实现任何愿望的人偶喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:18.16,0:18:20.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,任何愿望都可以实现…吗…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:23.46,0:18:26.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,亚由…我…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:26.20,0:18:29.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我到底该怎么做才好呢？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:36.24,0:18:39.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我没办法让奇迹什么的发生…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:41.18,0:18:44.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我没办法为名雪做任何事情吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:45.05,0:18:46.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只会糟蹋她的心情
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:46.58,0:18:47.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只会带给她痛苦的回忆
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:48.25,0:18:49.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这样子…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:49.89,0:18:52.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我是不是\N不要待在她身边比较好呢？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:52.29,0:18:54.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没有那种事情的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:55.56,0:18:56.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,亚由…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:57.16,0:18:59.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,亚由 你…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:59.20,0:19:02.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你放心 因为奇迹一定会发生的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:02.97,0:19:07.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,佑一是打从心底的\N想要帮助名雪对吧？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:08.01,0:19:10.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,比谁都还重视她的对吧？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:10.71,0:19:13.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可是那是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:14.91,0:19:16.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那就一定会实现的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:16.51,0:19:18.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果佑一是真心的话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:19.48,0:19:23.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那个天使人偶\N会帮佑一实现愿望的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:23.99,0:19:26.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,笨蛋 这可是你的人偶啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:26.56,0:19:29.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是为了要实现你的愿望\N才给你的不是吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:29.46,0:19:30.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我已经不需要了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:31.10,0:19:34.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,能像这样与佑一再会\N就已经很幸福了嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:34.73,0:19:37.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就连原本绝对吃不到的鲷鱼烧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:37.37,0:19:38.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,也吃了很多嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:39.30,0:19:40.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真的这样好吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:41.11,0:19:43.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你自己没有愿望吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:43.71,0:19:45.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我的…愿望…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:46.11,0:19:48.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是啊 你的愿望
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:48.35,0:19:50.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,任何愿望都可以吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:50.42,0:19:51.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,当然
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:51.82,0:19:53.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真的是真的吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:53.18,0:19:55.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真的是真的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:58.69,0:20:00.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那么…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:01.03,0:20:03.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我最后的…愿望…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:08.03,0:20:10.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,请把我…忘记吧…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:11.70,0:20:14.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,请把我的一切忘记
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:14.17,0:20:18.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,请把我当作从一开始\N就不曾存在过一样
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:22.05,0:20:25.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,请把我…忘记吧…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:25.25,0:20:27.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这样真的好吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:27.35,0:20:30.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,亚由的心愿就是被我遗忘吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:32.02,0:20:33.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不可能忘的吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:33.86,0:20:36.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你认为我能忘吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:39.76,0:20:42.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不能一直在这个城市吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:43.50,0:20:45.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真的就这样道别了吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:47.57,0:20:49.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,亚由…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:49.94,0:20:52.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,佑一 闭上眼睛…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:56.18,0:20:59.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,佑一 长久以来真的很感谢你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:20.21,0:21:22.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,亚由…已经走掉了吗…？
